    "shortDescription": "<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl00_LabelName\">While protected by <em>fastidiousness</em>, your person and your equipment stay clean and dry. Dust and moisture slough off immediately; even when you are completely soiled, your appearance reverts to a pristine state over the course of 1 minute. While this spell offers no protection against most attacks, staying constantly sanitary grants you a +2 circumstance bonus on Fortitude saving throws against inhaled and ingested diseases.</span></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl00_LabelName\">Members of the Prophet of Kalistrade prestige class can cast this spell, even though it is not a divination or enchantment.</span></p>"
